gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 124, Clippers 117
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bucks defeated the Clippers, 124-117. Damian Lillard recorded 35 points (7-13 3PT FG), 7 rebounds and 11 assists for the Bucks, while Giannis Antetokounmpo added 34 points, seven rebounds and 10 assists in the victory. Norman Powell put up 26 points and seven rebounds for the Clippers in the losing effort. The Bucks improve to 42-23 on the season, while the Clippers fall to 41-22.
